    <item>
      <title>拉马福萨计划设想南非成为建筑工地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-19/ramaphosa-announces-economic-vision-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨表示，他的新多党政府将优先考虑经济增长，通过进行结构性改革、整顿管理不善的市政当局、减少繁文缛节和增加基础设施投资。彭博新闻社的詹妮弗·扎巴萨贾与 Joumanna Bercetche 就中东和非洲视野进行了讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-19/ramaphosa-announces-economic-vision-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 08:43:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿布扎比马斯达尔计划在 10 亿美元交易后发行更多绿色债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/abu-dhabi-s-masdar-plans-more-green-bonds-after-1-billion-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿布扎比的主要可再生能源公司马斯达尔计划在未来几年每年发行绿色债券，为其全球扩张提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/abu-dhabi-s-masdar-plans-more-green-bonds-after-1-billion-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 08:40:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度储备银行行长称，印度储备银行需要“明确”关注通胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/rbi-needs-to-unambiguously-focus-on-inflation-governor-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度央行行长沙克提坎塔·达斯表示，由于经济增长依然强劲，印度央行需要“明确”关注通胀，这增强了人们对利率将在较长时间内维持不变的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/rbi-needs-to-unambiguously-focus-on-inflation-governor-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 08:39:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Capitec 称银行系统在全球中断后已恢复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/capitec-of-south-africa-says-its-systems-hit-by-global-outage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非客户数量最多的银行 Capitec 银行控股有限公司 (Capitec Bank Holdings Ltd.) 表示，在全球大规模计算机故障导致全球航空公司和银行业务中断数小时后，该行已成功恢复所有银行服务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/capitec-of-south-africa-says-its-systems-hit-by-global-outage</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 07:49:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
